criteria.description: Non-text Content: Provide text alternatives for non-text content
Contrast (Minimum): 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text, 3:1 for large text
Contrast (Enhanced): 7:1 contrast ratio for normal text, 4.5:1 for large text
Non-text Contrast: 3:1 contrast ratio for UI components and graphics
Keyboard: All functionality available via keyboard
No Keyboard Trap: Focus can move away from any component
Focus Visible: Keyboard focus indicator is visible
Language of Page: Primary language is specified
On Focus: No unexpected context changes on focus
Name, Role, Value: UI components have accessible names and roles
